These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-1::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: quad-bike, car, van, helicopter, bike, taxi, snowmobile
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, colombian, french, dutch, russian, egyptian, pakistani
 1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the egyptian##1
 2. the indonesian is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the russian is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the dutch##1
 6. the person driving the van is on the left of the dutch##1
 7. the russian is on the left of the indonesian##1
 8. the pakistani is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 9. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is the colombian##1
11. the person driving the helicopter is between the french and the person driving the van##2
12. the russian is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |   5   |    6     |    7    |
| Transport   | taxi  | helicopter | van  | bike | quad-bike | car | snowmobile |
| Nationality           | french | colombian   | pakistani | dutch  | egyptian   | russian    | indonesian    |

