.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: pop, metal, folk, soul, country, jazz, trance
There 7 different types of food: watermelon, nectarine, carrot, raspberry, papaya, cucumber, onion
 1. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
 2. the fan of metal is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 3. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person eating cucumber is in the middle##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 7. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
 8. the fan of soul is between the person eating papaya and the person eating nectarine##2
 9. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
10. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
11. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |      4      |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Music-Genre      | folk | soul | jazz   | metal | trance | pop     | country |
| Food   | nectarine     | watermelon  | papaya | cucumber     | onion  | carrot | raspberry |

