 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is the person playing canasta##1
10. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
11. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
12. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |         3          |     4      |      5       |      6      |    7     |
