 7. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
 8. the cape-cod house is between the tower house and the american##2
 9. the american is on the right of the colombian##1
10. the cottage house is on the left or right of the polish##3
11. the tower house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
