.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-20::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: video-games, card-games, filmmaking, baking, magic-tricks, sudoku, board-games
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: iris, tulip, daffodil, lily, sunflower, orchid, daisy
 1. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
 4. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
 5. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growstulip is between the person who growssunflower and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
 8. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
10. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
11. the person who growstulip is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

